query:
UPDATE products SET categoryId = (SELECT id FROM categories WHERE slug = 'sun-sign-guardians') 
WHERE (name LIKE '%Aries Guardian Pendant%' OR name LIKE '%Taurus Guardian Pendant%' 
OR name LIKE '%Gemini Guardian Pendant%' OR name LIKE '%Cancer Guardian Pendant%'
OR name LIKE '%Leo Guardian Pendant%' OR name LIKE '%Virgo Guardian Pendant%'
OR name LIKE '%Libra Guardian Pendant%' OR name LIKE '%Scorpio Guardian Pendant%'
OR name LIKE '%Sagittarius Guardian Pendant%' OR name LIKE '%Capricorn Guardian Pendant%'
OR name LIKE '%Aquarius Guardian Pendant%' OR name LIKE '%Pisces Guardian Pendant%')
AND name NOT LIKE '%Moon Crescent%';
